uws.service.backup

Class DefaultUWSBackupManager.JSONObjectReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • uws.service.backup.DefaultUWSBackupManager.JSONObjectReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<java.lang.String>
    Enclosing class:
    DefaultUWSBackupManager

    protected static final class DefaultUWSBackupManager.JSONObjectReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<java.lang.String>
    Lets reading a JSON object from a JSONTokener (that's to say directly from a file), as an iterator which returns all the keys. The value of each key can be fetched thanks to the different available getters (i.e. getJSONArray(), getJSONObject(), getValue(), getString(), ...).
    Version:
    05/2012
    Author:
    Grégory Mantelet (CDS)
